org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata
Class Dimension

java.lang.Object
  org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata.Meta
      org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata.Dimension

public class Dimension
extends Meta

Stores internal information of a dimension. This class is an image of 'dimension' tag from metadata XML, giving a complete information set about a single dimension in a data warehouse project.

The information includes:

  • table - the name of table containing data for this dimension
  • primary - the name of the primary key of dimension's table
  • foreign - the foreign key in facts table to which links this dimension
  • default - UID of the default hierarchy in this dimension
  • hierarchies - an array of hierarchy UIDs that belongs to this dimension

This component extends Meta class inheriting basic meta element properties from it (unique ID, name and description).
